.NET Framework 4.0.name: SharpDox.Model.Documentation
.NET Framework 4.0.description: The SharpDox.Model.Documentation namespace contains all types for parsing the inline documentation. SDDocumentation represents an inline documentation with all it members. For example the summary or example tag. Every property of SDDocumentation is a list of documentation tokens. For more information please see SharpDox.Model.Documentation.Token.

types.name: SDDocumentation
types.summary: Represents the inline documentation of a code member.

types.name: SDLanguageItemCollection
types.summary: Represents a collection of language specific elements.
